1. *Kakvu* ti poruku šalješ? (What kind of message are you sending?)

2. Mi treba *kakvu* drugu informaciju? (Do we need any other information?)

3. *Kakvu* ste boju izabrali? (What color did you choose?)

4. Želim da znam *kakvu* odluku ćeš doneti. (I want to know what decision you will make.)

5. Koliko puta ćete dobiti *kakvu* pomoć? (How many times will you get any kind of help?)

6. Da li ste čuli *kakvu* vrstu muzike? (Have you heard any kind of music?)

7. Da li imate *kakvu* ideju? (Do you have any idea?)

8. *Kakvu* vrstu pića želite? (What kind of drink do you want?)